declare @n integer declare @id1 uniqueidentifier declare @id2 uniqueidentifier begin if not exists(select 1 from instance where instanceid=@NumeratorID) insert into instance(instanceid,name,objtype) values(@NumeratorID,'Numerator','STDNumerator')
if not exists(select 1 from num_zones where zonemask=@zone and instanceid=@NumeratorID) begin set @num =1 set @ID1 = newid() set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_zones(num_zonesid,instanceid, zonemask) values(@id1,@NumeratorID, @zone) insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @num) return end else begin select @ID1=num_zonesid from num_zones where zonemask=@zone and instanceid=@NumeratorID if not exists(select 1 from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1 ) begin set @num =1 set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @num) return end else begin select @n = max(value)+1 from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1 set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @n) set @num = @n end end end

Set Obj.Author = RowItem.Application.FindRowObject("Users", Item.Application.MTZSession.GetSessionUserID()) Obj.TheDate = Date
If ReportType = "CLNT" Then Set Obj.Client = RowItem.Application End If If ReportType = "PRJ" Then Set Obj.Project = RowItem.Application End If If ReportType = "CONT" Then Set Obj.Contract = RowItem.Application End If If ReportType = "PERS" Then Set Obj.Person = RowItem.Application End If
Obj.Save RowItem.Save
Exit Sub bye: MsgBox Err.Description, vbOKOnly + vbCritical, "Создание отчета"

declare @n integer declare @id1 uniqueidentifier declare @id2 uniqueidentifier begin if not exists(select 1 from instance where instanceid=@NumeratorID) insert into instance(instanceid,name,objtype) values(@NumeratorID,'Numerator','STDNumerator')
if not exists(select 1 from num_zones where zonemask=@zone and instanceid=@NumeratorID) begin set @num =1 set @ID1 = newid() set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_zones(num_zonesid,instanceid, zonemask) values(@id1,@NumeratorID, @zone) insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @num) return end else begin select @ID1=num_zonesid from num_zones where zonemask=@zone and instanceid=@NumeratorID if not exists(select 1 from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1 ) begin set @num =1 set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @num) return end else begin set @n=null select @n = min(value) from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1 and value+1 not in (select value from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1) if @n is null select @n = max(value)+1 from num_values where parentStructRowID=@ID1 else select @n = @n + 1 set @ID2 = newid() insert into num_Values(num_valuesid,parentstructrowid, Value) values(@id2,@ID1, @n) set @num = @n end end end

declare @parent varchar(255) declare @prev varchar(255)
declare @tmpID uniqueidentifier declare @tmpRowID uniqueidentifier
declare @s nvarchar(4000)
-- checking session -- if not exists( select 1 from session where sessionid=@cursession and closed=0 ) begin raiserror('Session expired',16,1) if @@trancount>0 rollback tran return end
set @parent =@table set @tmpID = @ROWID
again:
set @prev = @parent set @parent = null select @parent =value from sysoptions where optiontype = 'parent' and name=@prev
--print @parent
if @parent is null begin set @s = N'select @root=InstanceID from ' + @prev + N' where ' +@prev + N'id=@id' -- print @s exec sp_executesql @s,N'@root uniqueidentifier out,@id uniqueidentifier',@tmpRowID out,@tmpid set @InstanceID=@tmpRowID end else begin set @s = N'select @parent=ParentStructRowID from ' + @prev+ N' where ' +@prev + N'id=@id' -- print @s exec sp_executesql @s,N'@parent uniqueidentifier out,@id uniqueidentifier',@tmpRowID out,@tmpid set @tmpID = @tmpROWID goto again end

update instance set LockUserID = null, LockSessionID=null where instanceID=@ID

declare @pr int, @allow int
if @resource is null begin set @access =1 return end
declare tst cursor READ_ONLY for SELECT MTZSEC_RIGHT.Allow, MTZSEC_RIGHT.Piority FROM MTZSEC_RIGHT INNER JOIN GroupUser ON MTZSEC_RIGHT.TheGroup = GroupUser.ParentStructRowID INNER JOIN [Session] ON GroupUser.TheUser = [Session].Usersid where [Session].Sessionid = @cursession and [Session].closed=0 and MTZSEC_RIGHT.InstanceID =@resource and MTZSEC_RIGHT.ProtectedItem =@verb order by MTZSEC_RIGHT.Piority open tst
FETCH NEXT FROM tst INTO @Allow,@pr if (@@fetch_status >= 0) BEGIN set @access =@allow CLOSE tst DEALLOCATE tst return END
set @access =0 CLOSE tst DEALLOCATE tst

if exists( select 1 from session where sessionid=@cursession and closed=0) begin declare @n nvarchar(4000) declare dl cursor for select N'update '+ value+' set LockSessionID =null where LockSessionID=@cursession' from sysoptions where optiontype='MAP' and Value not like 'V[_]%' open dl fetch next from dl into @n while @@fetch_status >=0 begin exec sp_executesql @n,N'@CURSESSION uniqueidentifier',@CURSESSION fetch next from dl into @n end close dl deallocate dl update INSTANCE set LockSessionID =null where LockSessionID=@cursession update session set closed=1,closedAt=getdate(), changeStamp=getdate() where sessionid=@cursession End

declare @sid uniqueidentifier declare closer cursor for select sessionid from session where lastaccess < (getdate()-0.01) and closed =0 open closer fetch next from closer into @sid while @@fetch_status >=0 begin print @sid exec Logout @sid fetch next from closer into @sid end close closer deallocate closer

declare @ID uniqueidentifier declare @USERSID uniqueidentifier declare @sysid uniqueidentifier
set @sysid = null select @sysid=instanceid from instance where objtype = 'MTZSYSTEM'
set @session=null
if @PWD is null begin
if exists( select 1 from users where Login=@usr and Password is null) begin select @usersid=USERSID from users where Login=@usr and Password is null set @id = newid() if @sysid is null insert into session(sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate())
else insert into session(instanceid,sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@sysid,@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate()) set @session=@id End
end else begin
if exists( select 1 from users where Login=@usr and Password=@PWD) begin select @usersid=USERSID from users where Login=@usr and Password=@PWD set @id = newid() if @sysid is null insert into session(sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate())
else insert into session(instanceid,sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@sysid,@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate()) set @session=@id End else if exists( select 1 from users where DomaiName=@usr and @PWD='INTEGRATED' ) begin select @usersid=USERSID from users where DomaiName=@usr set @id = newid() if @sysid is null insert into session(sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate())
else insert into session(instanceid,sessionid,lastaccess,usersid,closed,startAt) values(@sysid,@id,getdate(),@usersid,0,getdate()) set @session=@id End
end -- password is null
